NAME

    App::eachperl - a wrapper script for iterating multiple perl binaries

SYNOPSIS

       $ eachperl exec -E 'say "Hello"'
    
         --- perl5.30.0 --- 
       Hello
    
         --- bleadperl --- 
       Hello
    
       ----------
       perl5.30.0          : 0
       bleadperl           : 0

DESCRIPTION

    For more detail see the manpage for the eachperl(1) script.

AUTHOR

    Paul Evans <leonerd@leonerd.org.uk>

